-An-Nam-qu%E1%BB%91c-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%A5t-nguy%E1%BB%87t-tam-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-IpnNdoOg4z0geRUK_2t-kw">Thọ An Nam quốc vương thất nguyệt tam nhật - 壽安南國王七月三日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-SdALrlg8daTfB8oNiho-Nw">Lê Tắc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-fZekov0n38p16zJzIaCBWA">Thu dạ hoài ngâm - 秋夜懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ninh-T%E1%BB%91n/Tr%E1%BA%A5n-t%E1%BB%B1-du-t%C4%83ng/poem-iYtMAaUP_twuN4AzULyEuQ">Trấn tự du tăng - 鎮寺遊僧</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ninh-T%E1%BB%91n/author-0zxx9ptNwfX9AYtkCUmYYQ">Ninh Tốn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
